[[File:Tar_Sandstone_California.jpg|thumb]]

'''油砂'''（{{lang-en|Oil sands}}，亦称'''焦油砂'''）是一种[[黏土|黏土]]、[[水|水]]、[[石油|石油]]和[[沥青|沥青]]的混合物，是一種膠狀的黑色物質、{{le|非常規石油|Unconventional oil}}。約兩噸的油砂才能提煉出一桶原油，油砂含油量約佔本身兩成左右。焦油砂占据了世界石油储量的66%，主要分布在[[加拿大|加拿大]]。

==各地开采与使用==
目前加拿大的估計可採量達3150億桶以上，僅次於[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]之原油蘊藏量。目前加拿大每天能開採約100萬桶原油，未來計劃提升至每天200萬桶原油的數量。

[[台灣中油|台灣中油]]公司於2008年和加拿大當地的印地安油砂公司合作，雙方簽署8億加元投資的[[備忘錄|備忘錄]]將合作開採油砂。<ref>{{cite news|first= |last= |authorlink= |author= 禾楓云|coauthors= |title= 加原住民重視與台簽訂開採油砂備忘錄|trans_title= |url= http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/8/7/25/n2204250.htm|format= |work= |publisher= 中央社；大紀元（代）|location= |id= |pages= |page= |date= 2008-07-24|accessdate= 2016-01-05|language= |quote= |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20190612225749/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/8/7/25/n2204250.htm|archivedate= 2019-06-12|dead-url= no}}</ref>

2013年，美国拟為[[拱心石輸油管道|拱心石輸油管道]]擴建專門運輸油砂的管線<ref>{{cite news|first=|last=|authorlink=|author=Matthew Daly|coauthors=|title=TransCanada: Pipeline would not affect climate|trans_title=|url=http://www.cnsnews.com/news/article/transcanada-pipeline-would-not-affect-climate|format=|work=|publisher=|location=|id=|pages=|page=|date=2013-02-19|accessdate=2016-01-05|language=|quote=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306123618/http://www.cnsnews.com/news/article/transcanada-pipeline-would-not-affect-climate|archivedate=2016-03-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=|last=|authorlink=|author=林玉鵬|coauthors=|title=美加油管興建計畫 引發大規模示威|trans_title=|url=http://scitechvista.most.gov.tw/zh-tw/feature/c/0/3/10/1/172.htm|format=|work=科技大觀園|publisher=科技部|location=|id=|pages=|page=|date=2013-03-13|accessdate=2016-01-05|language=|quote=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305004525/http://scitechvista.most.gov.tw/zh-tw/feature/c/0/3/10/1/172.htm|archivedate=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，稱之為「XL工程」；正當参议院拟投票為工程开绿灯之時<ref>{{cite news|first= |last= |authorlink= |author= |coauthors= |title= Flashpoint Issue 2015: Keystone XL Tar Sands Pipeline|trans_title= |url= http://ens-newswire.com/2014/12/29/flashpoint-issue-2015-keystone-xl-tar-sands-pipeline/|format= |work= |publisher= Environment News Service|location= Washington, DC.|id= |pages= |page= |date= 2014-12-29|accessdate= 2016-01-05|language= |quote= |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20151213163437/http://ens-newswire.com/2014/12/29/flashpoint-issue-2015-keystone-xl-tar-sands-pipeline/|archivedate= 2015-12-13|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first= |last= |authorlink= |author= 環境資訊中心|coauthors= |title= 共和黨重掌國會 美加跨境油管或將起死回生|trans_title= |url= http://e-info.org.tw/node/104394|format= |work= |publisher= 台灣環境資訊協會|location= |id= |pages= |page= |date= 2014-12-29|accessdate= 2016-01-05|language= |quote= |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305000530/http://e-info.org.tw/node/104394|archivedate= 2016-03-05|dead-url= no}}</ref>，因其对环境影响极大而遭油管沿線地區民眾嚴重抗議，在不到24小时內集合了60万份请愿书<ref>{{Cite web|url= http://act.350.org/sign/kxl-ien/|title= Tell Your Senators: Reject the Pipeline!|accessdate= 2016-01-05|last= |first= |coauthors= |date= |work= |publisher= {{link-en|350.org|350.org}}|archive-date= 2016-03-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304210936/http://act.350.org/sign/kxl-ien/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。最終，時任总统[[奧巴馬|奧巴馬]]在諮詢過當地農民及[[美洲原住民|原住民]]部落的意见后，否決了油砂管線工程。<ref>{{cite news|first= |last= |authorlink= |author= |coauthors= |title= President Obama rejects Keystone XL Pipeline|trans_title= |url= http://www.vermontbiz.com/news/november/president-obama-rejects-keystone-xl-pipeline<!-- Vermont Business Magazine-->|format= |work= |publisher= Vermont Business Magazine|location= |id= |pages= |page= |date= 2015-11-06|accessdate= 2016-01-05|language= |quote= |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20190706141700/https://vermontbiz.com/news/november/president-obama-rejects-keystone-xl-pipeline|archivedate= 2019-07-06|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first= |last= |authorlink= |author= 經濟部／駐波士頓辦事處經濟組|coauthors= |title= Keystone XL石油管線建造案被否決|trans_title= |url= http://www.trademag.org.tw/News.asp?id=677673<!--http://www.taiwantrade.com.tw/CH/bizsearchdetail/8081488/CKeystone-->|format= |work= 經貿透視雙周刊|publisher= 台灣經貿網|location= |id= |pages= |page= |date= 2015-11-13|accessdate= 2016-01-05|language= |quote= |archiveurl= |archivedate= }}{{Dead link}}</ref>

